   <text>
      <body>
         <div><pb facs="#facs_1" n="1" xml:id="img_0001"/><fw type="page-number" facs="#facs_1_r" place="top">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_28" n="N001"/>3</fw>
               <hr/>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_1" type="Body">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l" n="N001"/>the shocking affair of the Dutch steam-ship "Friesland" which
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_1" n="N002"/>so nearly cost us both our lives. His cold and proud nature was
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_3" n="N003"/>always averse however to anything in the
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_2" type="scratched_out">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_29" n="N001"/><hi style="text-decoration: line-through;">shape</hi>
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_3" type="scratched_out">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_30" n="N001"/><hi style="text-decoration: line-through;">nature</hi>
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_4" type="floating">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_2" n="N001"/>shape
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_15" type="Body">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_31" n="N001"/>of public
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_4" n="N002"/>applause and he bound me in the most stringent terms to say no
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_5" n="N003"/>further word of himself, his methods or his successes - a prohibition
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_7" n="N004"/>which, as I have explained, has only 
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_5" type="floating">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_6" n="N001"/>now
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_6" type="scratched_out">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_32" n="N001"/><hi style="text-decoration: line-through;">just</hi>
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_16" type="Body">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_33" n="N001"/>been removed.
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_8" n="N002"/><rs type="person" wikiData="Q4653">Mr. Sherlock Holmes</rs> was leaning back in his chair
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_11" n="N003"/>after his whimsical protest, and was 
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_7" type="scratched_out">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_10" n="N001"/><hi style="text-decoration: line-through;">unfolding</hi>
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_9" type="scratched_out">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_34" n="N001"/><hi style="text-decoration: line-through;">opening</hi>
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_8" type="floating">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_9" n="N001"/>unfolding
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_10" type="floating">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_12" n="N001"/>^
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_17" type="Body">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_35" n="N001"/>his morning paper in a
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_13" n="N002"/>leisurely fashion when our attention was arrested by a tremendous
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_14" n="N003"/>ring at the bell, followed immediately by a hollow drumming sound
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_15" n="N004"/>as if someone were beating on the outer door with his fist. As it
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_16" n="N005"/>opened there came a tumultuous rush into the hall, rapid feet
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_18" n="N006"/>clattered up the stair and an instant later a wild eyed 
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_11" type="">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_17" n="N001"/>and frantic
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_12" type="floating">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_19" n="N001"/>^
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_18" type="Body">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_36" n="N001"/>young man,
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_20" n="N002"/>pale, dishevelled and palpitating burst into the room. He looked
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_21" n="N003"/>from one to the other of us and under our gaze of inquiry he became
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_22" n="N004"/>conscious that some apology was needed for this tumultuous entry.
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_23" n="N005"/>"Im sorry, <rs type="person" wikiData="Q4653">Mr Holmes</rs>" he cried "You musn't
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_25" n="N006"/>blame me. I am nearly mad. <rs type="person" wikiData="Q4653">Mr. Holmes</rs>, I am 
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_13" type="floating">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_24" n="N001"/>the unhappy
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_14" type="floating">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_26" n="N001"/>^
            </ab>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r_19" type="Body">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_37" n="N001"/>John Hector
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_27" n="N002"/>Mc. Farlane"
            </ab></div>
